    "Installation guides for multiple Linux distributions and Windows Server versions",
    "Theory materials covering OS architecture, virtualization, security, and domain administration",
    "Scripts and automation tools for PDF generation from markdown sources",
    "VirtualBox and Docker virtualization tutorials",
    "Active Directory and OpenLDAP domain management guides",
    "Educational trivial game generator for assessment"
  ],
